cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a novel method for multi-view subspace clustering, which involves techniques from linear algebra, optimization, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves some natural language processing techniques, which could place it in cs.CL (Computation and Language) and some multimedia techniques, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia).
